     "execution_count": 2,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "random_profile = svvamp.GeneratorProfileSpheroid(n_v=9, n_c=5)\n",
    "random_profile"
   ]
  },

   "metadata": {},
